                "MWPC",
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The LASA detector consists of a",
                " cylindrical multiwire proportional chanber",
                " surrounded by E-dE- plastic scintillator pairs. The",
                " wire chanmer consisted of three concentric levels",
                " of wires which run parallel to the detector axis.",
                " The gas mixture used consisted of 90% argon and",
                " 10% methane. dE-detector of each pair was 3.2 mm",
                " thick and E-detector was a 25.4 mm thick."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The target bag contained deuterium gas, enriched to",
                " the 99.74% level. The target gas was at room",
                " temperature and pressure, which averaged 22.5C degr.",
                " and 744.1 mm Hg. The resultant number density for",
                " 2H was 4.86 x 10**19 nuclei/cm**3."
              ]
            }
          ],
